<div class="section-header">
    <h2 class="section-title">Help & User Guide</h2>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>Manager Dashboard Guide</h3>
    <p>Welcome to the Ocean View Resort Manager Dashboard. This guide will help you navigate and use all the features available to you.</p>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>1. Dashboard Overview</h3>
    <p>The dashboard provides a quick overview of the hotel's current status:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Total Rooms:</strong> The total number of rooms in the resort</li>
        <li><strong>Occupied Rooms:</strong> Number of currently occupied rooms</li>
        <li><strong>Available Rooms:</strong> Number of rooms available for booking</li>
        <li><strong>Today's Checkouts:</strong> Number of guests scheduled to check out today</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can also view recent reservations at a glance.</p>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>2. Reservations Management</h3>
    <p><strong>Create New Reservation:</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>Fill in guest details (name, contact, email, NIC)</li>
        <li>Select room type and number of guests</li>
        <li>Choose check-in and check-out dates</li>
        <li>Add any special requests</li>
        <li>Click "Create Reservation"</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p><strong>Search Reservations:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Use the search bar to find reservations by booking ID, guest name, or contact number</li>
        <li>Click "Search" to filter results</li>
        <li>Click "Clear" to reset the search</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><strong>Edit Reservation:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Click "Edit" button next to any reservation</li>
        <li>Modify the booking details as needed</li>
        <li>Click "Update Reservation" to save changes</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>3. Room Availability</h3>
    <p>View the status of all rooms in the resort:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Filter by Room Type:</strong> Use the dropdown to view specific room types</li>
        <li><strong>Room Statistics:</strong> See available/total rooms for each category</li>
        <li><strong>Room Details:</strong> View room number, floor, type, capacity, rate, view type, and status</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>4. Check-in / Check-out</h3>
    <p><strong>Today's Check-ins:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>View all guests scheduled to check in today</li>
        <li>Click "Check In" button to complete the check-in process</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><strong>Today's Check-outs:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>View all guests scheduled to check out today</li>
        <li>Click "Check Out" button to complete the check-out process</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><strong>All Active Bookings:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>View all confirmed and checked-in bookings</li>
        <li>Perform check-in or check-out for any booking</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>5. Cleaning Service Management</h3>
    <p>Manage the cleaning status of all rooms:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>View Statistics:</strong> See count of clean, cleaning, and dirty rooms</li>
        <li><strong>Update Status:</strong> Click "Update" next to any room to change its cleaning status</li>
        <li><strong>Status Options:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Clean:</strong> Room is ready for guests</li>
                <li><strong>Cleaning:</strong> Room is currently being cleaned</li>
                <li><strong>Dirty:</strong> Room needs cleaning</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>6. Billing</h3>
    <p><strong>Generate Bill:</strong></p>
    <ol>
        <li>View all checked-in or checked-out bookings</li>
        <li>Click "Generate Bill" next to the booking</li>
        <li>Review the invoice details</li>
        <li>Use "Print Invoice" to print the bill</li>
    </ol>
    
    <p><strong>Bill Components:</strong></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Room rate × Number of nights</li>
        <li>Service charge (10%)</li>
        <li>Tax (12%)</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>7. Navigation</h3>
    <p>Use the sidebar menu to navigate between different sections:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Click on any menu item to switch views</li>
        <li>The active section is highlighted</li>
        <li>Use "Exit System" to logout</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>8. Tips for Efficient Use</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Always verify guest information before creating reservations</li>
        <li>Check room availability before confirming bookings</li>
        <li>Update cleaning status promptly to ensure accurate room availability</li>
        <li>Generate and review bills before guest checkout</li>
        <li>Use the search function to quickly locate specific reservations</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="form-section">
    <h3>Need More Help?</h3>
    <p>If you encounter any issues or need additional assistance, please contact the system administrator or IT support team.</p>
    <p><strong>System Version:</strong> Ocean View Resort Management System v1.0</p>
</div>
